data.description: Come check out this beautiful turn of the century home! This 1900's build still has a lot of its original charm with solid wood doors and trim. On the main level, you will be greeted by a large dining room, a kitchen, half bath and a spacious living room with a fireplace. Upstairs you will find four bedrooms and a full bath. The upper most level provides great potential with the space being unfinished. Outside you will find a large fenced in yard and a one stall garage. Schedule a showing today! Come check out this beautiful turn of the century home!
